>
  <h2 id="configuration-file">Configuration File</h2>

  <p>
    Sinks are configured in <code>~/.datagenc/config.yaml</code>:
  </p>

  <pre><code>sinks:
  mysql:
    host: localhost
    port: 3306
    database: testdb
    username: root
    password: secret
  
  postgres:
    host: localhost
    port: 5432
    database: testdb
    username: postgres
    password: secret</code></pre>

  <h2 id="environment-variables">Environment Variables</h2>

  <p>Override configuration with environment variables:</p>

  <pre><code># MySQL
export DATAGENC_MYSQL_HOST=localhost
export DATAGENC_MYSQL_PORT=3306
export DATAGENC_MYSQL_DATABASE=testdb
export DATAGENC_MYSQL_USERNAME=root
export DATAGENC_MYSQL_PASSWORD=secret

# Postgres
export DATAGENC_POSTGRES_HOST=localhost
export DATAGENC_POSTGRES_PORT=5432
export DATAGENC_POSTGRES_DATABASE=testdb
export DATAGENC_POSTGRES_USERNAME=postgres
export DATAGENC_POSTGRES_PASSWORD=secret</code></pre>

